sql.sqlStatement:
SELECT 
  '{'                            as [Item], 
  'Capability Map'               as [Label], 
  'Capability Map'               as [Tooltip], 
  'Border 0 Begin'               as [style name], 
  'pack="12" packmode=array_ut2' as [attributes]

SELECT
  [1.Capability] & [2.Component] as [Item],
  [2.Component]                  as [Label],
  [1.Description]                as [Tooltip],
  [1.Domain]                     as [cluster],
  'Border 2 '                    as [cluster style name],
  [1.Capability]                 as [subcluster],
  'Border 4 '                    as [subcluster style name]      
FROM 
  [Capabilities$] AS 1,[Capability Mapping$] AS 2
WHERE
  [1.Capability] = [2.Capability]
ORDER BY [1.Domain],[1.Capability]

SELECT 
  '{'                            as [Item], 
  'Component Interface Overview' as [Label], 
  'Component Interface Overview' as [Tooltip], 
  'Border 0 Begin'               as [style name], 
  'pack="12" packmode=array_ut1' as [attributes]

SELECT 
  [Component]          as [Item],       
  'sortv=%rsc%'        as [attributes],
  [Component]          as [Label],
  [Description]        as [Tooltip],
  [Layer]              as [cluster],
  'Border 6 '          as [cluster style name],
  [Layer]              as [cluster tooltip],
  'sortv=%clc% packmode=array_utr3'     
                       as [cluster attributes],
  [Cluster]            as [subcluster],
  'Border %scc% '      as [subcluster style name],
  [Cluster]            as [subcluster tooltip],
  'sortv=%scc% packmode=array_utr3' 
                       as [subcluster attributes] 
FROM 
  [Components$] 
ORDER BY 
  [Layer Order]     ASC, 
  [Cluster] ASC

SELECT 
  [from]          as [Item],       
  [to]            as [Related Item],
  [Protocol] &": " & [Description]        as [Tooltip]
FROM 
  [Interfaces$]

SELECT 
  '{'                            as [Item], 
  'Deployment Overview'     as [Label], 
  'Deployment Overview'     as [Tooltip], 
  'Border 0 Begin'               as [style name], 
  'pack="12" packmode=array_ut1' as [attributes]

SELECT 
  '{'                            as [Item], 
  'Internet'     as [Label], 
  'Internet'     as [Tooltip], 
  'Border 1 Begin'               as [style name], 
  'sortv=1 pack="12" packmode=array_ut4' as [attributes]

SELECT DISTINCT
  [1.Region/DataCentre]&[1.Node]&[2.Component]          as [Item],
  [2.Component]                                         as [Label],
  [1.Region/DataCentre] & "_" & [1.Availability Zone]   as [cluster],
  'Border 2 '                                           as [cluster style name],
  'sortv=%clc% pack="12" packmode=array_ut2'            as [cluster attributes], 
  [1.Node]                                              as [subcluster],
  [1.Description]                                       as [subcluster Tooltip],
  'Border 4 '                                           as [subcluster style name],
  'pack="12" packmode=array_ut1'                        as [subcluster attributes]
FROM 
  [Nodes$] AS 1,[Deployment$] AS 2
WHERE
  [1.Node] = [2.Node] AND
  [1.Layer]='Internet'
ORDER BY [1.Region/DataCentre] & "_" & [1.Availability Zone], [1.Node]

SELECT 
  '{'              as [Item], 
  'On Premise'     as [Label], 
  'On Premise'     as [Tooltip], 
  'Border 1 Begin'               as [style name], 
  'sortv=2 pack="12" packmode=array_ut4' as [attributes]

SELECT DISTINCT
  [1.Region/DataCentre]&[1.Node]&[2.Component]          as [Item],
  [2.Component]                                         as [Label],
  [1.Description]                                       as [Tooltip],
  [1.Region/DataCentre] & "_" & [1.Availability Zone]   as [cluster],
  'Border 2 '                                           as [cluster style name],
  'sortv=%clc% pack="12" packmode=array_ut2'            as [cluster attributes], 
  [1.Node]                                              as [subcluster],
  [1.Description]                                       as [subcluster Tooltip],
  'Border 4 '                                           as [subcluster style name],
  'pack="12" packmode=array_ut1'                        as [subcluster attributes]
FROM 
  [Nodes$] AS 1,[Deployment$] AS 2
WHERE
  [1.Node] = [2.Node] AND
  [1.Layer]='On premise'
ORDER BY [1.Region/DataCentre] & "_" & [1.Availability Zone], [1.Node]

SELECT 
  '{'                            as [Item], 
  'Cloud'     as [Label], 
  'Cloud'     as [Tooltip], 
  'Border 1 Begin'               as [style name], 
  'sortv=3 pack="12" packmode=array_ut2' as [attributes]

SELECT DISTINCT
  [1.Region/DataCentre]&[1.Node]&[2.Component]          as [Item],
  [2.Component]                                         as [Label],
  [1.Description]                                       as [Tooltip],
  [1.Region/DataCentre] & "_" & [1.Availability Zone]   as [cluster],
  'Border 2 '                                           as [cluster style name],
  'sortv=%clc% pack="12" packmode=array_ut2'            as [cluster attributes], 
  [1.Node]                                              as [subcluster],
  [1.Description]                                       as [subcluster Tooltip],
  'Border 4 '                                           as [subcluster style name],
  'pack="12" packmode=array_ut1'                        as [subcluster attributes]
FROM 
  [Nodes$] AS 1,[Deployment$] AS 2
WHERE
  [1.Node] = [2.Node] AND
  [1.Layer]='Cloud'
ORDER BY [1.Region/DataCentre] & "_" & [1.Availability Zone], [1.Node]
